c: 3
v: 159
t: "Ne nikhulwa tsimbabaasi tsirulanga khu Nyasaye nitso tsichila noba omwihotselefu khubo, Ne obetsanga omululu, womwoyo omumu bakhakhwilushe. Khomana baleshele ne obasabile eshileshelo, ne sanjilana nabo mumakhuwa, Ne nomala wabusia, wisiche Nyasaye, toto Nyasaye yachama Abandu bamwisikanga"